file_a: A Critical Edition of the Bodhicittabhāvanā (based on bstan 'gyur versions).txt
text_a: ston pa ’jig rten sgron mar gyur pa kun gyis mtshungs par rab bsngags pa | | chos la chos kyi snying por gyur pa ’jam dpal gzhon nu snying po nyid | | bde gshegs ma lus yum du gyur pas rgyal ba kun gyi lam gcig go  | tshul khrims la sogs pha rol phyin lam spyod pa rgya mtsho’i gzhir gyur pa

file_a: A Critical Edition of the Bodhicittabhāvanā (based on bstan 'gyur versions).txt
text_a: phra zhing shes dka’ drang srong chen po’i lam ’di mi rtog rtog las ’das | | brtag par dka’ zhing bstan par dka’ la brjod pa’i tha snyad rnams dang bral | | (5) tshig gis mi phebs gzhan dang byis pa kun gyi spyod yul ma yin yang | | ston pa nges pa’i lung dang bla ma dam pa rnams kyi gdams ngag de nyid don ’dir blta | | mngon sum la sogs rgyu yis dngos po ’jig cing grub pa’i mtha’ dpyod pa | | de nyid rtog pa’i rgyun ’brangs
text_b: phra shing shes dka' kun gyi lam ste mi rtog rtog las 'das// mi gnas mi dmigs spros med bsam pa kun dang bral// tshig gis mi phebs dbyibs dang kha dog spyod yul med// bstan cing brtag par dka' la brjod du rdul tsam med// sngon gyi drang srong lam du gang zhugs pa// bsgom chags lam gyi nad kyis zin ta re// ston pa'i lung bzhin tshig gi mtha' spyod lam du de mthong na// de ni rtog pa'i rgyun 'brangs
